<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_9782b987-e88f-470d-8e56-08fb718e86a0" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="SA"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/></meta><sptc>H5D4</sptc><title id="_50043de1-57e6-4e2a-aeaa-a9a4771d9475">Minimum space between buildings</title><archive-num>2019: SA 6.2.1, 6.2.2</archive-num><subclause id="_55ed5d52-aa17-4af6-bd30-02c1a47f40b2" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_695cf8cf-6028-43c0-a4d3-62a3db2f6b5b">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Compliance with (2) for acceptable separation between buildings for Class 1 and 10 buildings satisfies <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1395_4.0.0.xml#_f7304862-3529-49d7-9f62-352bcbcb6294" id="_ca85b08e-042e-4185-92bd-a9777242d1fd" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Performance Requirement</xref> <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/7126_0.3.0.xml#_f4ff5c70-5c0c-4d33-8ca4-ff69503ad70c" id="_bccdd284-8095-4a7e-9c23-d9baf95be218" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">SA H5P3</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_62e0005d-2acc-460d-b6d3-695e373075e9" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_e6bb77c9-768e-457f-9fc6-b43b7d2878b3">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>Unless the space between external columns is not infilled, every part of an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1267_2.3.0.xml#_d87c7cc0-d0b0-40ab-9a5b-d070ed6e115e" id="_43183292-168f-42ec-b6b4-4651f5604630" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">external wall</xref> of a building must be not less than 600 mm from—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_818d36d3-2077-4914-a810-8e120dfda586">any boundary of the allotment, unless that wall is on or abutting that boundary; or</li><li id="_24cad57e-4387-4a42-beef-d752689ddba7">the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1267_2.3.0.xml#_d87c7cc0-d0b0-40ab-9a5b-d070ed6e115e" id="_55869c9a-616f-42b6-8fdf-86cbc8dcf84f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">external wall</xref> of any other building on the same allotment, unless the two buildings are abutting.</li></ol></subclause></clause>